    <briefdescription>
<para>Provides a utility macro for forcing the expansion of other macros. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides small helper macros for token forwarding and macro expansion in C++ codebases. These macros operate at preprocessing time and do not introduce runtime overhead. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
